<p>i have been using dispatchKeyEvent to get the keycode of android keyboard but the problem is when i tap on Sym or Emoji button nothing happen, no keycode shows. this is the code i use to get the keycode:</p>  <pre><code>@Override public boolean dispatchKeyEvent(KeyEvent event) {     Toast.makeText(getBaseContext(), "key pressed : "+ String.valueOf(event.getKeyCode()), Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();     return super.dispatchKeyEvent(event); } </code></pre>